description:
Minecraft Server. Today we start off by checking out how the new Wither Skeleton farm works. Beef calls us in for an odd meeting. We sneak a new shop called Sneak-E-E's into the shopping district. Bamboozler gets built at base. Then we face off in the Stand-Off minigame tournament.
